"Heartless" is a song by American hip hop artist Kanye West. It is the second single off West's album 808s & Heartbreak.[1] Much like the first single from the album, "Love Lockdown", the song features Auto-Tune-processed vocals. The single was released onto iTunes on November 24, 2008.
